node.text:
I made my Abuela's Berenjenas en Escabeche 🍆 (Pickled Eggplant) using my favorite jars @leparfaitworldwide 
This recipe is so easy to make and perfect for this time of the year 😋, click the link in my BIO for the recipe! 
And watch the video only on my IGTV, now!! 
💚
#pickled #eggplants #keepcookingbehappy #gabyskitchen #ad

node.text: I bought 2 bundles of spinach ( not bags) even the word bag which is plastic is so embedded in our head right? This is me trying to wash greens while doing other things, this is me trying to bring less plastic home! What’s your plastic worst nightmare? I am trying to be more minimal in my kitchen too. Watch it! You can save the water  for watering your plants! 😘

node.title: TIPS: Washing greens, talking plastic...basically me talking! 😂💚😉

node.text:
1 year ago today I posted this video of my Mom, a video she accidentally did back in June of 2014 when she got her first touchscreen cellphone and wanted to take a selfie; a Year and a half later she was gone! It took me months to finally empty her cellphone after she died and discover this silly moment we had and that I had forgotten all about it.
A year ago today in the middle of the most unforgettable year;  I decided that it was time for me to finally use my #youtube channel and that this was the best way to share her, being silly and me telling her “you need to wait a bit!” Which is rare, since I used to not like to wait! Waiting is a new skill I developed recently… waiting and sitting still…Hey Ma, guess what? I finally learned how to wait!!!!
So…a year ago I open my channel and on the same month I sent out my first newsletter, this simple actions opened another door, the one that made me step out of the giant glass tower and into the world! But that story is for another day 😉 
Cheers to glass towers, and you tube channels and ducking 2020 and waiting, I wish my Mom waited a few more years to take off and see where I am now! Te quiero Má! Estas en el cielo y en mi corazón para siempre! #mamivsalien 💚 #happymonday 
NEWSLETTER COMES OUT TOMORROW, go to my link⬆️ and sign up to receive it, so you can keep reading me! I mean that is only if you like to read, which I assume you do, if you are reading this post all the way to the end! 
🤣 #keepcookingbehappy #gabyskitchen #askgaby
